### Global Assets
- `posts/images/`: Directory for shared images used across multiple posts
- [posts/_metadata.yml](mdc:posts/_metadata.yml): Default metadata settings for all posts

## Build and Output
- `_site/`: Generated static website files (not tracked in git)
- `.quarto/`: Quarto's internal files and cache (not tracked in git)

## Version Control
- `.gitignore`: Specifies which files and directories should be ignored by git
- `.git/`: Git repository data
